Combat
When the player interacts with an enemy, the system shall initiate a combat interface within 2 seconds.

The combat interface shall display the user and the enemy facing each other.

The combat interface shall display user options in 4 buttons which will allow the user to attack, open bag, use skill, or run.
  The attack button shall initiate a default attack against the enemy
  The open bag button shall display the consumable items from the user's inventory that will aid in battle.
  The skill button shall display 4 buttons that represent different skills the user's character can use to attack or defend against the enemy or buffs the user.
  The run button shall make the user leave the battle.


